title: Septimus Heap Series PDF eBook & Audio Book Collection I-VI
description:
For your digital backup convenience, I have for you a collection of both Audio and eBooks in PDF format of Angie Sage Septimus Heap series. Books one through six have been included in this upload.

Originally I was going to include a summary of each book in this description. However, I have decided not to spoil this excellent story line for any readers. Instead below you will find links to Wikipedia for each as well as a general coverage of the entire series & the author Angie Sage.

Book 1 Magyk: <a href=" http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Magyk" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Magyk</a>
Book 2 Flyte: <a href=" http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flyte" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flyte</a>
Book 3 Physik: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Physik
Book 4 Queste: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Queste
Book 5 Syren: <a href=" http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Syren(book)" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Syren(book)</a>
Book 6 Darke: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Darke_%28novel%29
Book Author: <a href=" http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Angie_Sage" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Angie_Sage</a>
Entire Series: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Septimus_Heap
